<% @page_title = "Frequently Asked Questions" %>
<% @header_title = "Frequently Asked Questions" %>

<div class="faq">

<h2>What is tourb.us?</h2>

<p>A better way to find the live music in your area. Hear about shows ahead of time, 
get reminded when your favorite bands come to town and contribute to a community focused on live music.
We want to make it much easier for fans to see the bands they like and discover new music. 

<h2>Who can submit a show?</h2>

<p>Anyone who has signed up as a fan or registered their band can <%= link_to("add a show", :controller => "shows", :action => "add")%>.
And we definitely welcome submissions from anyone who wants to help promote their favorite band, club or scene. Our goal
is that tourb.us will have the most complete list of the live music around, and we'll need plenty of help to get there.

<h2>But my favorite band / club / city isn't listed!</h2>

<p>Initially we're focusing on the music scenes in <%= link_to("Boston", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "boston")%>, 
<%= link_to("Seattle", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "seattle")%>, <%= link_to("Austin", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "austin")%>,
<%= link_to("Chicago", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "chicago")%>, <%= link_to("Los Angeles", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "la")%>,
<%= link_to("New York", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "nyc")%> and the <%= link_to("Bay Area", :controller => "public", :action => "metro", :metro => "sf")%>, 
and are continuing to expand coverage. If you know of good lists of shows online 
in your area (like the website of a club or a scene), definitely let us know and we'll get it added post-haste! Unless it is for hippies. Oh ok, them too. 

<p>Any website that has a good list of shows can be added to our index. We don't require the information to
be in any special format, but if there good RSS or iCal feeds we can add those too.

<p>And <b>anyone</b> can <%= link_to("add a show", :controller => "shows", :action => "add")%>, which we most definitely
encourage. We need your help to build a better way to find great music by bands of any size!

<p>Also, right now, we're concentrating on the USA. Our apologies to the rest of the world. 

<h2>Hey, you've got my band listed - I want it!</h2>

<p>We find lots of bands when we collect shows from the web, and we might have found your band (which we've heard kicks ass).
If you'd like to claim it so that you can manage it, please send us mail at 
<a href="mailto:feedback@tourb.us">feedback@tourb.us</a> and we can get you set up. And if you're in a band we haven't
discovered yet, you can <%= link_to("signup your band", :controller => "signup", :action => "band")%> to list your shows.

<h2>Got anything for my blog, website or MySpace page?</h2>

<p>Why yes, we do, thanks for asking. We've got some of these little buttons if you're into that sorta thing.
Simply download the image (or copy this <a href="http://tourb.us/images/button.png">image link</a>), throw it up on your site with a link to your tourb.us profile.

<p><%= image_tag "button.png" %>

