<h2>We should collaborate and/or conspire!</h2>

<p>As long as it's legal in more than 42 states, we're interested. If you're a show promoter, 
club owner, musician, or just someone with a slightly crazy idea <a href="mailto:feedback@tourb.us">please get in touch</a>.

<h2>Any other questions, comments or suggestions?</h2>

<p>We're always excited to hear about how we could make the site better. We've got a 
  <a href="http://forum.tourb.us">discussion forum</a> available to post questions, bugs
  or feature requests. Or send us <a href="/feedback">feedback</a>
or an email at <a href="mailto:feedback@tourb.us">feedback@tourb.us</a>.

</div>